-1, otherwise its the wrong one. It can be obtained from Mitty in Kerra Isle, however my friend camped Mitty for 30 hours STRAIGHT and did not receive the ring ONCE. All he got was tons of coppers and one silver, no gold. He finally gave up as would anyone because I don't think its worth even the Paw of Opolla if you have to stay up for two days camping an 18 minute spawn. If anyone has this ring on the Prexus server and would like to sell it send me (Seijuro) or Toromn a tell.
